<arggraph id="micro_k009" topic_id="introduce_capital_punishment" stance="con">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Germany should by no means introduce capital punishment.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[If there were capital punishment,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[this would mean people are allowed to put themselves above others and rule over their lives.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Capital punishment would be murder]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[and would have to be punished with the death penalty itself.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[What, then, ought to be done with criminals who have committed truly awful crimes such as murder or rape -]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[should they simply be allowed to live on]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[although they have taken or destroyed another life?]]></edu>
  <edu id="e9"><![CDATA[Yes, for it is a much graver punishment to be imprisoned forever and be tortured by one's own thoughts than to be killed quickly and easily by an injection.]]></edu>
